errors_gamma2_20taxa <- unlist(lapply(reconstructions_20taxa_gamma, function (aux) 100*(1/stimes20[length(stimes20)]) * sum((aux$effpop - trajectory_bottleneck(aux$x))/trajectory_bottleneck(aux$x))))
